://www.danaos.com/investors/overview/default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Danaos Corporation</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DAC\" title=\"Danaos Corporation\">DAC</a>). Both companies are large players in the fixed-rate time charter market and are mostly focused on the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1409662027/image_1409662027.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742636-global-ship-lease-arbitraging-the-residual-value-of-older-containerships", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 18:37:16"}, {"id": "4742634", "title": "Bank Of Hawaii: Dominant And Undervalued", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1402278061/image_1402278061.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial of Bank of Hawaii Building\" data-id=\"1402278061\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1402278061/image_1402278061.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1402278061/image_1402278061.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1402278061/image_1402278061.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1402278061/image_1402278061.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1402278061/image_1402278061.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1402278061/image_1402278061.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1402278061/image_1402278061.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1402278061/image_1402278061.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.